<i>♪ The bell has been raised
from its watery grave</i>

43
00:05:05,832 --> 00:05:09,165
<i>♪ Hear its sepulchral tone</i>

44
00:05:10,403 --> 00:05:15,397
<i>♪ A call to all
Pay heed the squall</i>

45
00:05:23,850 --> 00:05:27,286
<i>♪ Turn your sails to home</i>

46
00:05:29,422 --> 00:05:31,447
<i>♪ Yo ho</i>

47
00:05:32,158 --> 00:05:34,126
<i>♪ Haul together</i>

48
